Oddbins Asks Court for Protection From Creditors, Times Says

-- B y   J o h n   G l o v e r
-- 
2011-03-27T10:27:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-27/oddbins-asks-court-for-protection-from-creditors-times-says.html
Oddbins Properties Ltd., the
unprofitable U.K. wine retailer, asked a court for protection
from its creditors to gain time to hold a meeting to decide its
future, the Sunday Times said, citing the company.  Creditors on March 31 will vote on whether to approve a so-
called company voluntary arrangement under which they will
receive about 21 percent of their claims, compared with 7
percent if the company goes into administration, the newspaper
said.  Click here for web link.   To contact the reporter on this story:
